Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.09,0:09:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无数的梦让我浮想联翩\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}A million dreams are keeping me awake.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.22,0:09:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在想世界会变成什么样\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I think of what the world could be.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.60,0:09:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我将会看到怎样的一个精彩的世界\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}A vision of the one I see.{\r}
