Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.69,0:09:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将由我们编织成完美的世界\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}A million dreams for the world we're gonna make.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.16,0:10:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管它是大还是小\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}However big, however small.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.41,0:10:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我融为其中\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Let me be part of it all.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.71,0:10:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起分享着你我的梦想\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Share your dreams with me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.38,0:10:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你或许是对的 又或是错的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You may be right, you may be wrong.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.42,0:10:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你带着我一起\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}But say that you'll bring me along.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.14,0:10:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向着眼前的世界前进\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}To the world you see.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.48,0:10:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,闭着眼睛 用心感受\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}To the world I close my eyes to see.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.69,0:10:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我闭上双眼\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I close my eyes to see{\r}
