Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.57,0:10:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脑海中满是缤纷的思绪\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}The brightest colors fill my head.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.79,0:10:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无数的梦想激励我前行\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}A million dreams are keeping me awake.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.62,0:10:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无数的梦想\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}A million dreams, a million dreams.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.42,0:10:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在想世界会变成什么样\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I think of what the world could be.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.63,0:10:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我将会看到怎样的一个精彩的世界\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}A vision of what I see.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.84,0:10:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无数的梦想交织在一起\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}A million dreams is all it's gonna take.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.39,0:11:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将由我们编织成完美的世界\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}A million dreams for the world we're gonna make.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.32,0:11:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了我们将创造的这美好世界\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}For the world we're gonna make.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.21,0:11:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 史密斯先生 - 是我\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- Mr. Smith? - Yeah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.25,0:11:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来看看这个\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Have a look at this, here?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.35,0:11:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的我看到了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Yes, yes, I see it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.44,0:11:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 查默斯 这个可以\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Thank you, Chalmers, that will do.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.28,0:11:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生 我是菲尼亚斯·泰勒·巴纳姆\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Sir. Phineas Taylor Barnum.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.11,0:11:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果愿意听我讲讲的话 先生\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}If I may sir,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.38,0:11:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得我有才华 很有想法\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I believe I have skills and ideas...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.56,0:11:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不应该把自己限制在操作加法机上\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}that go well beyond counting numbers into an adding machine.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.61,0:11:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在报纸上读到了这个德国人的故事 他叫利林塔尔\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I have read about this German fellow, Lilienthal...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.85,0:11:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他发明了一种滑翔机\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I believe he's developed a glider{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.41,0:11:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能把人送上天 先生\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}that could take a man in the air, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.98,0:12:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样很棒的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Isn't that amazing?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.29,0:12:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果能把这个技术投入实际运用\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I mean, if you were to apply that to this business,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.61,0:12:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将是具有革命性的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}it would be revolutionary.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.76,0:12:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生 请注意 你们都被解雇了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Gentlemen. Can I have your attention? You are all dismissed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.93,0:12:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,破产了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Bankrupt?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.93,0:12:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我听说公司有很多商船呢\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I thought the company had a dozen trading ships.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.43,0:12:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 沉到南中国海的海底去了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Yes, at the bottom of the South China Seas.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.06,0:12:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刮了台风 全沉了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}A typhoon sank them all.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.94,0:12:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 抓住你了 - 你在这儿呢\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- Tinker it. - Oh, you're in for it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.10,0:13:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 嘿 - 我的天 你回家早了啊\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- Hey. - Oh God. You are home early.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.82,0:13:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看看这个\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}And until further notice.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.57,0:13:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是不觉得你愿意干那份工作\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Oh I didn't think you were along for that job.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.66,0:13:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别的工作也不怎么感兴趣啊\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Or any job apparently.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.54,0:13:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那让我们在一起的生活更有意思了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}That's what makes our life together so exciting.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.41,0:13:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏瑞蒂\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Charity.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.17,0:13:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我答应给你的生活 不是这个样子的 - 但我想要的都有了啊\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- This isn't the life I promised you. - But I have everything I want.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.92,0:13:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 但这生活没有意思啊 - 这两个女孩是你的什么人\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- What about the magic? - What do you call those two girls?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.97,0:13:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孩子们 看谁来了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Hey, you partners, look who.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.66,0:13:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Daddy!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.90,0:13:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 来 - 你给我带了礼物么\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- Come here. - Did you bring a present?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.58,0:13:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么礼物\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Present, for what?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.78,0:13:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我的生日啊 - 你的什么\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- For my birthday. - Your what?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.78,0:13:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我的生日 - 这不是你的生日\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- My birthday. - It's not your birthday.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.44,0:13:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过没事 我这有一份礼物\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Okay, I do have a present.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.47,0:13:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但这可不是普通的礼物\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}But not just any present. Oh no.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.49,0:13:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这可是最棒的生日礼物\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}The most amazing birthday present ever.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.91,0:13:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这台巧夺天工的机器最早\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}This extraordinary machine was originally{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.44,0:13:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是400年前由列奥纳多·达·芬奇制造的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}created by Leonardo Da Vinci 400 years ago.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.88,0:13:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是机器的蓝图消失了好几个世纪\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}But the blueprints have been lost for centuries,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.15,0:14:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到上周 那是一个风暴交加的夜晚\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}until just last week, on a stormy night...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.04,0:14:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一辆沉没海盗船的残骸 冲上了楠塔基特岛的岸边\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}when a sunken pirate ship washed up on the shores of Nantucket.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.97,0:14:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人们发现骷髅 财宝\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}They found skeletons and treasures...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.15,0:14:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有由"JW商业公司"发现的一幅机器蓝图\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}and the blueprints were recovered by none other than JW Mercantile.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.27,0:14:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,机器的蓝图在我这停留的时间不长\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}The blueprints crossed my desk very briefly...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.77,0:14:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我试着将它记了下来\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}but I managed to commit them to memory...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.77,0:14:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我记得没错的话\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}and if I had remembered correctly...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.58,0:14:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生日快乐 卡洛琳\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Happy birthday, Caroline.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.55,0:14:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是一台许愿机器 你对它许愿\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}This is a wishing machine. You tell it your wishes...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.80,0:14:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它会记录下你们的愿望 一直到愿望实现\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}and it keeps them safe until they come true.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.76,0:14:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算你们忘了 那些愿望还是会留在这里\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Even if you forget them, they are always there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.56,0:14:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我能许愿么 - 走上前来 开始吧\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- Can I tell a wish? - Step right up. Go ahead.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.40,0:15:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我希望能嫁给圣诞老人 - 你这个愿望好\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- I wish to marry Santa Clause. - That is a good wish.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.03,0:15:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想要一双芭蕾舞鞋\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I wish for ballet slippers.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.83,0:15:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这个愿望也不错\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Hey, that's a good wish too.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.63,0:15:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么愿望么 妈咪\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}What is your wish, Mommy?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.96,0:15:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I wish...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.22,0:15:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们能像这样 永远幸福\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}for happiness like this forever.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.26,0:15:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们两位\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}For you and you...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.11,0:15:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有你的父亲 都幸福\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}and for your father.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.98,0:15:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 无聊 - 无聊\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- Boring. - Boring?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.48,0:15:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幸福的日子怎么会无聊呢\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Since when is happiness ever been boring?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.86,0:15:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每晚我躺在床上\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Every night I lie in bed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.95,0:15:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脑海中满是缤纷的思绪\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}The brightest colors fill my head.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.16,0:15:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无数的梦想激励我前行\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}A million dreams are keeping me awake.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.83,0:15:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在想世界会变成什么样\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I think of what the world could be.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.25,0:15:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我将会看到怎样的一个精彩的世界\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}A vision of the one I see.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.55,0:16:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无数的梦想交织在一起\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}A million dreams is all it's gonna take.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.85,0:16:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将由我们编织成完美的世界\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}A million dreams for the world we're gonna make.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.46,0:16:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,山羊的价格上升了 五花肉的价格下跌了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}The goat prices go up, so the pork bellies go down.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.12,0:16:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 查尔斯 我们走 - 怎么了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- Charles, we're leaving. - Huh?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.42,0:16:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,银行只借钱给有钱人\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}This bank only wants to lend money to people with money.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.39,0:16:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看什么看\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}What are you looking at Flop Doodle?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.14,0:16:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴纳姆先生\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Mr. Barnum.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.27,0:16:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你提出的这个项目风险很大 而且有点奇怪\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}This venture you propose is risky and somewhat bizarre.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.02,0:16:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这个项目其实挺好的 先生 人们只是不愿意相信罢了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}It's a good bet, it's what it is. Sir, people don't wanna admit it...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.57,0:17:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是那些异国情调的和恐怖的展品能吸引观众\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}but they are fascinated with the exotic and the...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.28,0:17:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我主要关注的是这个\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}is why we stare at it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.08,0:17:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,银行需要你提供大量的抵押物作担保\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}The bank is going to need substantial collateral.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.21,0:17:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然 不然也不会借钱给我了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Of course. I would not suggest otherwise.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.25,0:17:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我名下有一支商船队 这里是契据及业权\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}The deed and title to my entire fleet of trading vessels.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.22,0:17:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么银行会借给我们1万美元\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Why would a bank loan us 10,000 dollars?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.17,0:17:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我提供给了他们担保物\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Because we put up collateral.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.79,0:17:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我们没有什么担保物啊\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}We don't have any collateral.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.47,0:17:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然有的 在南中国海呢\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Sure we do. In the South China Seas.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.79,0:17:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 南中国海 - 在南中国海海底呢\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- In the South China Seas? - Deep in the South China Seas.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.38,0:17:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们打算用这笔钱购置什么吗\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}And what did we buy with this loan?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.63,0:17:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美国巴纳姆奇物博物馆\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Barnum's American Museum of Curiosity.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.68,0:17:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么博物馆啊\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}What kind of museum is it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.18,0:17:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会改造这里\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}A place to be transported.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.13,0:17:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这里人们会看到前所未有的新奇事物\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}A place where people can see thing they've never seen before.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.73,0:17:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 蜡像么 - 对\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- Wax figures? - Yeah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.73,0:17:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是欧洲产的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}They are all the rage in Europe. Look.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.69,0:17:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗓子痛的玛丽亚·安东尼特\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Marie Antoinette with the sore throat.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.94,0:17:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有拿破仑 过来 看到了么\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Napoleon. Come here. You see?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.04,0:17:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们已经见过了历史上几个有名的人物了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You have already met some of the most famous folks from the history.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.99,0:17:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不止是蜡像而已\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}But they are not all wax.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.75,0:18:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这位是奥马利先生\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}This is the Great O'Malley.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.10,0:18:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戏法之王 擅长瞒天过海\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Master of sleight of hand, the king of deception.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.79,0:18:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你看起来可不像魔法师啊 - 我是个贼\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- You don't look like a magician. - I am a thief.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.79,0:18:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很厉害的贼 他偷我手表的时候我抓住他了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}A very good thief. I caught him taking my watch.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.01,0:18:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 看到了没 - 那有大象\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- You see? - An elephant.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.13,0:18:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 那可不是普通的大象\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Not just any elephant.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.64,0:18:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会让你刮目相看的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I'll get you something real nice to say the word.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.31,0:18:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 谢谢 - 这玩意可有10吨重\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- Thank you. - Oh yeah. This is a ten ton bulls...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.80,0:18:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从非洲平原弄来的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}straight from the plains of Africa.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.18,0:18:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看那个\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}And, look at that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.18,0:18:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 世界上最高的长颈鹿 - 我能顺着它的腿爬上去么\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- The tallest giraffe in the world. - Can I climb up its leg?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.91,0:18:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绝对 不行\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Absolutely no. OK.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.06,0:18:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我知道现在是个什么情况 - 如果你不知道的话 我会很担心的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- Now, I know how it looks. - If you didn't, I would be worried.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.60,0:18:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要努力一下了 不过...\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I mean it just needs a little work..{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.24,0:18:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每个月要还贷的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}The loan has to be paid back every month.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.05,0:18:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会还的 需要观众而已\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Oh yeah, we're gonna pay. We just need customers.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.82,0:18:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 要很多的观众 - 会有的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- Hundreds of them. - We're gonna get them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.70,0:18:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到巴纳姆博物馆 参观一小时\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Welcome to the Barnum Museum. It is one hour of your time, sir...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.63,0:18:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次经历会改变你的一生\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}but it will change your life.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.27,0:18:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任意时间均可参观\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}We have a shows on the hour, every hour.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.25,0:18:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你的裙子\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I love your dress.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.88,0:18:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不推荐胆子小的人去看 但是你们会喜欢上那里的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Surely not for the fainted heart. I can tell you that you'll love it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.96,0:18:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戴帽子的顾客半价\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Half the price for anyone who is wearing a hat.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.15,0:18:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是你了 先生\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Ho ho, That's you, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.20,0:18:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到巴纳姆博物馆\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Welcome to the Barnum Museum.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.56,0:19:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是垃圾\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Garbage.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.77,0:19:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到巴纳姆博物馆 顾客呢\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Welcome to the Barnum Museum, where everyone...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.67,0:19:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卖出去多少张票\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}How many tickets?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.11,0:19:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 三张 - 三张?\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- Three. - Three?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.64,0:19:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Daddy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.47,0:19:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Daddy?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.23,0:19:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你今天有没有卖出去更多的票 - 卖出去一些了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- You sell anymore tickets today? - A few. Yeah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.70,0:19:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,周五了 大家急着回家\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Most of 'em was rushing home, it's Friday.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.28,0:20:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卖出去一些了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}We sold a few.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.99,0:20:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 我觉得你的博物馆里死的东西太多了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I think you have too many dead things in your museum daddy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.98,0:20:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是么\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Do you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.37,0:20:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她说得对 我们要一些活的东西\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}She is right. You need something alive.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.72,0:20:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你们俩去睡吧 - 要一些能引发轰动的东西\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- Go to sleep, both of you. - Something sensational.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.30,0:20:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你们用的这个词很大啊 - 那是你用过的词\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- That is a big word. - That's your word.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.06,0:20:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要那些不是填充标本的东西\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Something that isn't stuffed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.06,0:20:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 比如美人鱼 - 独角兽\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- Like a mermaid. - Or a unicorn.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.90,0:20:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 独角兽不存在的 - 美人鱼也不存在的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- Unicorns aren't real. - Well, mermaids aren't real either.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.30,0:21:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您是格特鲁德·斯特拉顿吧\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You must be Gertrude Stratton.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.34,0:21:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要找您的儿子\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I am looking for your son.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.43,0:21:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有儿子\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I don't have a son.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.85,0:21:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,医院的档案上写着 你有一个儿子啊\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}The hospital record says you do.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.15,0:21:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是叫查尔斯吧 22岁\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Charles, right? Age 22?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.24,0:21:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,查尔斯\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Charles.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.30,0:21:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是P·T·巴纳姆 愿意为您效劳\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}P. T Barnum. At your service.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.55,0:21:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在组织一个剧团\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I'm putting together a show...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.94,0:21:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,需要一位明星演员\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}and I need a star.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.22,0:21:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家会笑话我的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You want people to laugh at me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.18,0:21:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎样他们都会笑话你的 至少我们能赚到钱嘛\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Well, they are laughing anyway, kid. So, might as well get paid.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.36,0:21:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我眼前浮现出一位士兵 不 一位将军\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I see a soldier. No, a general...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.80,0:22:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走过舞台 手里拿着剑和枪\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}riding across the stage with a sword and gun and...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.74,0:22:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身着最为精致的制服\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}and the most beautiful uniform ever made.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.25,0:22:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全世界的人们来到这里\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}People will come from all over the world{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.34,0:22:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们不会笑话你\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}and when they see him they won't laugh.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.09,0:22:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们会向你敬礼\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}They will salute.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.30,0:22:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,需要 奇特之人 浮夸的表演 世界奇人\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Wanted! Unique persons, curiosities. Daring acts. Wonders of the world.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.78,0:22:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起来怎么样 孩子们\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}How is it looking girls?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.70,0:22:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在找那些怪胎么\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Hey. You looking for freaks?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.43,0:22:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道上哪能找到\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I know where you can find one of them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.54,0:22:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是么\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Really?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.00,0:22:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 孩子们\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Come on, girls.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.92,0:23:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你好 - 先生你不能进来\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- Hello. - Sir, you can't be here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.46,0:23:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉 唱歌的这位是谁\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I'm sorry. Who is doing that singing?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.14,0:23:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是你吧\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}It's you, isn't it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.60,0:23:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 请您离开 先生 - 你真是很有天分...\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- Sir, I'll have to ask you to leave. - You are so talented, blessed...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.98,0:23:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太奇妙了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Extraordinary.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.70,0:23:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很奇特\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Unique.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.41,0:23:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我甚至能用漂亮这个词来形容你\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I would even say 'beautiful'.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.49,0:23:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Sir,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.48,0:23:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请不要打扰我\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}please leave me alone.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.05,0:23:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们现在不理解你 但他们以后会的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}They don't understand it, but they will.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.61,0:23:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安 和 W.D. 惠勒\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}OK. Anne and WD Wheeler.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.18,0:24:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你们是兄妹么 - 是的 先生\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Brother and sister?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.06,0:24:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的 你们有什么特殊技能么\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- Yes sir. - Terrific. And what do you do?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.58,0:24:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我们会玩空中飞人 - 空中飞人\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- Trapeze. - Trapeze. OK.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.36,0:24:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是你让我们登台演出的话 估计公众反响会不太好\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You know, people aren't gonna like it if you put us on the stage.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.16,0:24:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就指望着这点呢\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Oh, I am counting on it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.44,0:24:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你的... - 整个身体\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- Is this so far your... - Entire body.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.31,0:24:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不错 不用全部展示给我看了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Fantastic. I don't need to see it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.19,0:24:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,*纹身男\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Tattoo Man Barnum Museum.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.23,0:24:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,*狗男\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Dog boy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.98,0:24:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能问问你有多重么\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Can I just ask how heavy you are?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.71,0:24:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能告诉我么\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Do you have a number for that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.23,0:24:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我觉得还是不说比较好 - 我不会说出去的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- I prefer not to say it, but... - Just between you and me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.27,0:24:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,500磅\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}500 pounds.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.86,0:24:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 750磅? 你是说750磅么 - 750磅\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- 750 pounds? Is what you said? - 750 pounds!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.16,0:24:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,*世界上最肥胖的男人\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}World's heaviest man.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.42,0:24:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你叫什么名字？ - 先生您好 我叫瓦西里·帕洛斯\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- What's your name? - Vasily Palvos, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.79,0:24:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这名字得改一下\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Yeah, we are going to change that name.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.36,0:25:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得你是爱尔兰人\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I think you're Irish.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.64,0:25:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,*爱尔兰巨人\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Irish Giant.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.38,0:25:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这阵容绝对够用了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}We have a show.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.89,0:25:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很不错 海报的版面再翻五倍\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}That's good, but I need it five times bigger.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.38,0:25:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有地方都贴上海报\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}And I want it everywhere.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.74,0:25:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马车上 火车侧面上 手推车上 墙上\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Carriages, sides of trains, trolleys, crates...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.67,0:25:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牛奶瓶上 满世界都是海报\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}milk bottles, everywhere they look.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.84,0:25:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴纳姆美国博物馆\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Barnum's American Museum.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.48,0:25:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你过得磕磕绊绊\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Nice to see you, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.66,0:25:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直低着头\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You stumble through your days. Got your head hung low.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.78,0:25:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,漫天阴云不散\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Your skies' a shade of Grey.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.12,0:25:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-  如僵尸于迷宫内蹒跚 - 两张票 谢谢\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Like a zombie in a maze. - Two, please.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.79,0:25:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你内心昏沉 但仍可听见希望的呼唤\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You're asleep inside But you can shake awake.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.58,0:25:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为你只是行尸走肉\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}'Cause you're just a dead man walking Thinking that's your only option.{\r}
