Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.34,0:31:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你兜售的这些噱头都是假的 难道你不愧疚吗？\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}does it bother you that everything you're selling is fake?{\r}
