Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.74,0:32:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不都是这个原因啦\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}That was not the only reason.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.82,0:32:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我承诺过要给你的生活\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}This is the life I promised you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.12,0:32:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们跳舞吧\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Shall we?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.56,0:33:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菲尼亚斯\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Phin...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.96,0:33:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这房子是很漂亮 但是我们真的不用...\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}It's beautiful, but we don't need all of this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.12,0:33:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经25年了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}It took me 25 years, but...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.17,0:33:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回家 夏瑞蒂·巴纳姆\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Welcome home, Charity Barnum.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.92,0:33:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你好 - 巴纳姆来了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- Hello there! - Barnum is in.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.38,0:33:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个小伙子是谁？\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Hey, sweetie, who is that young man over there?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.06,0:34:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是菲利普·卡莱尔 人们都说他是骗子\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}That is Philip Carlyle. A bit of a scandal, they say.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.80,0:34:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他上次在伦敦的表演很成功\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- His last play was a hit in London. - Play?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.91,0:34:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人们花好大一笔钱\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Pay good money to{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.44,0:34:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就愿意看台上的人叨叨2个小时 他们居然好意思说我是骗子\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}watch people stand around and talk for two hours, and they call me a con man.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.65,0:34:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么味啊？ 你闻到了吗？\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Ew. What's that smell? Do you smell that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.86,0:34:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 真恶心 这味确实够难闻的 - 我知道了 是花生（谐音P.T巴纳姆的P 讽刺巴纳姆一家）\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- Ew, something does smell. - I know what it is. Peanuts.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.62,0:34:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经看到你的未来了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I can see it right now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.33,0:34:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你将会是都市芭蕾舞剧历史中最年轻的芭蕾女舞蹈家\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}"Youngest prima ballerina in the history of the City ballet."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.21,0:34:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我不想跳芭蕾了 - 什么？为什么不想跳了？\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- I'm quitting. - What? Why would you quit?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.39,0:34:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我学的太晚了 永远也别想跟上他们的高度\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I started too late. I will never catch up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.29,0:34:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡洛琳 你是舞台上跳的最好的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Caroline, you were the best dancer on that stage.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.64,0:34:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得我看不出谁有天赋吗？\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}What? Do you think I can't spot talent?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.35,0:34:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想跳好芭蕾须数年苦练 跟马戏团不是一回事\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Ballet takes years of hard work. It's not like the circus.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.02,0:34:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坑蒙拐骗是行不通的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You can't just fake it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.87,0:35:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她不能放弃 不对 我是说她不该放弃\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}She can't quit. No. No, I mean... She doesn't.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.54,0:35:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她只是觉得有人排挤她了而已\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}She just feels out of place with the other girls.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.55,0:35:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也希望如此\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Well, I should certainly hope so.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.91,0:35:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这辈子可 没见过这么多自以为是的人\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I have never seen so many little prima Donnas in my life.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.53,0:35:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些自以为是的人\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Yes, but those prima Donnas are the most{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.14,0:35:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在对小卡洛琳来说非常重要\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}important thing in the world to her right now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.77,0:35:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她得学会无视那些人 我小时候就这么干的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}She'll learn to ignore them, just like I did.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.39,0:35:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她不是非得如此\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}She shouldn't have to.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.77,0:35:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,纽约社会永远不会真心接纳我们\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}New York society will never accept us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.81,0:35:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些人一天天的 不对我们品头论足\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}If they did, they'd have to stop judging...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.90,0:35:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都不知道怎么继续过日子了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}and actually do something with their lives.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.46,0:35:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这事不能往我身上扯\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}This isn't about me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.84,0:35:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是说这事的起因跟其他的不一样喽？\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Oh... So it's different than everything else then?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.43,0:35:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是希望她因是我们家庭的一份子而感到自豪\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I just want her to be proud of who she is, of her family.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.35,0:35:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她很自豪\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}She is proud.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.13,0:35:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不必非得变成卡莱尔家那样\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}We don't have to be the Carlyle's.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.44,0:35:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡莱尔先生 这部戏是你制作的？\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Mr. Carlyle. You produced this play?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.19,0:35:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Yes I do, indeed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.84,0:35:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,退票去售票处\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Refunds are available at front box office.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.41,0:35:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我是P·T·巴纳姆 - 开马戏团的那个?\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- P.T. Barnum. - From the circus?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.81,0:35:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 对 你看过我的演出?\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Yes. You've been?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.56,0:35:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊 我可没看过 但我见过你的团队成员\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}God, no. But I've seen the crowds.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.29,0:35:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人们看完你的演出后都很开心\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}People leave your show happier than when they came in.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.27,0:36:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比我的戏有意思多了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Which is much more than I can say from my play.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.69,0:36:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你票可不愁卖啊\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}And yet, you have no trouble selling tickets.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.30,0:36:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为我的卖点是节操\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}That's because I'm selling virtue.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.35,0:36:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能请你跟我喝一杯吗？\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Can I buy you a drink?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.67,0:36:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想要争取到高端群众\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I want to go after the carriage straight.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.28,0:36:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加入正剧情节 扩大影响力\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Present legitimate acts, expand our appeal...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.36,0:36:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,专门针对那些势利小人\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}go after the snobs.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.43,0:36:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要是知道这帮人多难缠的话就不会...\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}If you only knew how suffocating they are.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.95,0:36:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加入我的马戏团吧\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}So come join our circus.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.34,0:36:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很明显你在娱乐圈很有眼光\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You clearly have a flair for show business.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.40,0:36:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,教我如何吸引更多的关注度\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Teach me how to appeal to the highbrows.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.28,0:36:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你认真的？\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Are you serious?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.72,0:36:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴纳姆先生 我不能就这么简单地跑到你那加入你的团队\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Mr. Barnum, I can not just run off enter into circus.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.42,0:36:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不行？听着不是挺好么\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Why not? Sounds thrilling isn't it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.00,0:36:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就当我能毫无心理压力地在远处\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Lets just say that I find it much more comfortable...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.18,0:36:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 欣赏着你的表演 - 心理舒适 那是进步的绊脚石\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- admiring your show from afar. - Comfort, the enemy of progress.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.62,0:36:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要知道 哪怕我只是辅助你\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Do you understand that just associating with you{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.57,0:36:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也会丢掉遗产继承权的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}could cost me my inheritance.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.11,0:36:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你丢掉的可不止这个\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I thought it'd cost you more than that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.80,0:36:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这就是孤注一掷\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You would be risking everything.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.04,0:36:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是从另一个角度来看的话呢\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}But, on the other hand, well,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.06,0:36:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以认为你得到了自由\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}you just might find yourself a free man.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.55,0:36:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,此时此地\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Right here, right now I put the offer out.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.55,0:37:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我像你发出邀请\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I don't want to chase you down I know you see it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.97,0:37:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想死缠烂打 我相信你也看到光明的前景\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You run with me. And I can cut you free.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.28,0:37:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你我并肩 向自由前行\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Out of the drudgery and walls you keep in.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.40,0:37:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不受束缚 摆脱监禁\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}So trade that typical for something colorful.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.84,0:37:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忘掉固有 迎向缤纷未来的降临\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}And if it's crazy, live a little crazy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.13,0:37:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,活得疯狂一点又如何\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You can play it sensible, a king of conventional.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.26,0:37:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以循规蹈矩\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Or you can risk it all and see.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.20,0:37:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也可以放飞自我 亲自去见证\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Don't you wanna get away from{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.12,0:37:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你难道不想逃离这墨守成规的人生\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}same old part you gotta play.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.25,0:37:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有你所需\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}'Cause I got what you need.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.88,0:37:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 跟我去兜风\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}So come with me and take the ride.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.88,0:37:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,体验所有的不同\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}It'll take you to the other side.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.38,0:37:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以一成不变 也可以想我看齐\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}'Cause you can do like you do Or you can do like me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.47,0:37:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以选择牢笼 也可摆脱掌控\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Stay in the cage, or you'll finally take the key.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.63,0:37:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你终得悠然翱翔于天空\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Oh, damn! Suddenly you're free to fly.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.35,0:37:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,体验所有的不同\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}It'll take you to the other side.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.69,0:37:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的朋友 你想和我并肩\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Okay, my friend, you want to cut me in.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.60,0:37:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可我只能给你泼冷水 因为这些都不会发生\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Well I hate to tell you, but it just won't happen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.69,0:37:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心领了 但是不可能\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}So thanks, but no. I think I'm good to go.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.28,0:38:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想我该离开了 你所说的束缚 我还享受其中\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}'Cause I quite enjoy the life you say I'm trapped in.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.36,0:38:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很钦佩 你和你的演出\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Now I admire you, and that whole show you do.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.53,0:38:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的眼光很准 直觉很灵\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You're onto something, really it's something.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.54,0:38:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我们属于不同的世界 可谓泾渭分明\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}But I live among the swells, and we don't pick up peanut shells.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.76,0:38:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只能劝你别纠缠不清\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I'll have to leave that up to you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.29,0:38:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还不懂吗\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Don't you know that I'm okay with{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.58,0:38:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我无所谓我现在做的事情\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}this uptown part I get to play.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.49,0:38:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已拥有一切 不会同你前行\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}'Cause I got what I need and I don't want to take the ride{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.04,0:38:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想体验你所谓的不同\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I don't need to see the other side.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.02,0:38:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以继续奋斗 我会回到我的生活\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}So go and do like you do. I'm good to do like me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.40,0:38:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不须摆脱什么 因为没有束缚我的牢笼\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Ain't in a cage, so I don't need to take the key.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.57,0:38:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 难道你看不出我过得悠闲自在？\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Oh, damn! Can't you see I'm doing fine?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.06,0:38:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想体验你所谓的不同\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I don't need to see the other side.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.32,0:38:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你想要的日子？\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Now is this really how you like to spend your days?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.65,0:38:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,酗酒纵情 苦乐不知\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Whiskey and misery, and parties and plays.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.99,0:38:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我跟你混 会成为人们茶余饭后的谈资\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}If I were mixed up with you, I'd be the talk of the town.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.28,0:38:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卑微不堪 自欺欺人的傻子\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Disgraced and disowned, another one of the clowns.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.85,0:38:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你的人生会多一些欢笑 多一些真实\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}But you would finally live a little, finally laugh a little.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.50,0:38:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以给你梦想的自由\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Just let me give you the freedom to dream and it'll wake you up{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.71,0:39:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,睁开双眼 治愈心灵的伤痛\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}and cure your aching.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.29,0:39:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,摆脱桎梏 摧毁樊笼\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Take your walls and start 'em breaking.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.83,0:39:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的这份提议 应值得认同\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Now that's a deal that seems worth taking.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.14,0:39:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我会让你自己做决定\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}But I guess I'll leave that up to you.{\r}
