Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.09,0:39:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生 很荣幸成为你的合作伙伴\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Sir, it looks like you have yourself a junior partner.{\r}
