Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.95,0:41:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 嘿 飞一半怎么就回来 去前台完成表演\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Hey. No one is buying hats back here. Get out front, go.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.04,0:41:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来 W·D·惠勒  安·惠勒  我给你们介绍一下 这是我新雇来的 他叫菲利普·卡莱尔\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}WD, Anne, I want to introduce my newest hire, Mr Philip Carlyle.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.63,0:41:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 很荣幸见到你 - 我也是\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- It's a pleasure to meet you. - Yeah, pleasure.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.92,0:41:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么绝活？ 卡莱尔先生\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}And what is your act, Mr. Carlyle?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.93,0:41:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有绝活\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I don't have an act.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.85,0:41:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里每个人都有绝活的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Everyone has got an act.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.23,0:41:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 巴纳姆先生 - 怎么了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- Mr. Barnum. - Yeah?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.90,0:41:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你最好过来看一下\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You better come see this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.10,0:41:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菲利普 过来啊\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Philip, keep up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.16,0:41:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 真糟糕啊 - 一直都是这样啊\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- A bit of nasty element. - They're always is, isn't it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.91,0:41:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,世间任何群体的存在都会有其他群体抵触\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Nothing draws a crowd crying like a crowd.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.78,0:41:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滚回家怪物们\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Go home you freaks.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.75,0:41:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,城市的污点\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}"Shame of the city".{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.34,0:41:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抗议者们认为巴纳姆先生的名誉\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}"The protests amend Mr. Barnum's reputation..."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.27,0:41:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是建立在经营无礼和下流的基础上的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}"as a previewer of the offensive and indecent."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.37,0:42:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无礼和下流 本内特先生 我都脸红了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}"Offensive and indecent." Mr. Bennett, I'm blushing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.17,0:42:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才脸红了呢\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}No, I'm blushing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.96,0:42:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁在乎本内特说什么\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}What do you care what Bennett thinks?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.85,0:42:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他是个混蛋 - 势利小人一个\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- He's a prick. - And a snob.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.61,0:42:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 全纽约的势力眼们都看到他的评语了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Yeah, all the snobs in the New York are reading me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.58,0:42:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他很会迎合这帮人\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Does their thinking for them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.98,0:42:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不过是他一家之言\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}What ever happened to the thriving of controversy?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.13,0:42:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这话倒是没错\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Yeah, well... Look, hey..{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.84,0:42:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这事你有什么看法？ - 菲利普\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- Do you have any thoughts on this? - Philip.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.71,0:42:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 事实上 我确实有 - 海伦 别闹了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- As a matter of fact, I do. - Helen, come on.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.73,0:42:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宫务大臣受女王旨意\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}"The master of the Household, has it in the command of the Queen...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.89,0:42:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,邀请P·T·巴纳姆先生 及其剧场团队成员参加\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}To invite Mr. Phineas T Barnum and his theatrical{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.03,0:42:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白金汉宫的招待会\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}troop to a reception at Buckingham Palace."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.50,0:42:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 真是维多利亚女王的邀请？ - 我动了点私人关系\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- The Queen Victoria? Is this real? - I had to pull a few strings.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.84,0:42:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要社会接纳你们\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}If you want society to accept you,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.56,0:42:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最好从最高端人群下手\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}you may as well start at the very very top.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.01,0:42:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们都在受邀之列吗？\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Are we all invited?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.44,0:42:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想我只能跟女王说这些人要么全去\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I guess I'll just have to tell the queen either all of us go{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.94,0:42:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要么谁也不会去\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}or none of us will.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.26,0:43:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英国女王 这真是再好不过了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}The Queen of England. Can't get much better than that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.33,0:43:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 为什么我们不穿燕尾服 - 因为我们是来表演的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- Why aren't we in tails? - We are the entertainment.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.28,0:43:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是只想穿戏服的吗？\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I don't see you in a costume.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.88,0:43:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女王陛下  来自美国的P·T·巴纳姆\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Your Majesty, Mr Phineas T Barnum and his...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.97,0:43:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和他的...奇葩伙伴\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Oddities from America.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.35,0:43:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是真的么\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Is that real?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.12,0:43:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女王陛下 请允许我向您介绍 巴纳姆先生\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Your Majesty, may I present Mr Barnum.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.79,0:43:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,见到您是我的荣幸 巴纳姆先生\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}The honor is mine, Mr. Barnum.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.00,0:44:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的美国朋友跟我说了很多\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}And I've heard all about your little colonel{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.96,0:44:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关于你那个小上校的事情\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}from my friends in America.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.96,0:44:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是将军 女王陛下\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}General, ma'am.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.36,0:44:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他比我想得还玲珑一些\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You are even smaller than I imagined.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.24,0:44:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您也不算是大个子啊 亲爱的女王\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Well, you are not exactly reaching the top self yourself sweetheart.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.58,0:44:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切还算顺利\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Ah, that went well.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.79,0:44:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 女王陛下 - 菲利普\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- Your Majesty. - Philip.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.12,0:44:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,珍妮·琳德女士\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Miss Jenny Lind.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.29,0:44:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是光彩照人\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}She is really luminous.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.84,0:44:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 她是谁？ - 歌剧演唱家\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- Who is that? - The opera singer.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.26,0:44:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,演唱家？\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Singer, huh?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.85,0:44:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是享誉全欧洲的表演家\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}She is the most famous performer in all of Europe.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.93,0:45:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她在斯卡拉歌剧院（米兰著名歌剧院）表演过很多次\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}She has sold out La Scala a dozen times.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.56,0:45:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更不用提她演唱过的法国歌剧了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Not to mention the French Opera.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.86,0:45:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太漂亮了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Striking.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.12,0:45:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你这是干什么？ - 跟着你啊\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- What are you doing? - Following you...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.58,0:45:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 这样你就能把我介绍给林德女士了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}so you can introduce me to Miss Lind.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.43,0:45:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 介绍你？ - 对啊\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- Introduce you? - Yeah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.50,0:45:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都不认识她\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I don't know her.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.61,0:45:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都认识她 你自己都这么说了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Everybody knows her. You just said so yourself.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.06,0:45:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 对啊 你不能就这么直接过去..\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Yeah, exactly. You don't just walk up to someone right now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.88,0:45:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么不行的 我是人 她也是\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Why not? We are presentable. She is a person.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.42,0:45:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,林德女士 我叫菲利普·卡莱尔\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Miss Lind. My name is Phillip Carlyle.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.42,0:45:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我身边这位杰出的男士是...\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}And this extraordinary gentleman next to me...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.69,0:45:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菲尼亚斯·泰勒·巴纳姆 见到您 我荣幸之至\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Phineas Taylor Barnum. The pleasure is mine.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.59,0:45:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 你是那个美国人 我想我可能听说过你\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Of course, you are the American. I believe I might have heard of you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.06,0:45:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你在这么远都听过在下微名\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Oh well, If you've heard of me all the way over here,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.45,0:45:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这说明我干的还不错\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I must have been doing something right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.52,0:45:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也有人说是非常烂\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}That, or something very wrong.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.96,0:45:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舆论界观点不一\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}In the world of publicity there is hardly any difference.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.24,0:45:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴纳姆先生 媒体都说你是个骗子呢\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I believe those are the words of a scoundrel, Mr Barnum.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.13,0:45:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马戏团老板 林德女士 我是大西洋对岸最好的马戏团老板\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}A showman, Miss Lind, just a showman. The best on my side of the Atlantic.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.28,0:46:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我想你只是在自夸 - 我是在夸自己 但我是什么样的人不用我自己说\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- If you just say so yourself. - I do, but I don't have to.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.79,0:46:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是 他确实是顶尖之一呢\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Oh, no, no. He is one of the best.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.67,0:46:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢 林德女士 我就直说了吧\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}That's very kind of you. Miss Lind, let me get to the point.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.71,0:46:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想带您去纽约 如果你同意的话\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I would like to bring you to New York. And if you agree...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.18,0:46:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会让你不只是享誉全欧洲的女歌唱家 更是享誉全世界的女歌唱家\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I will make you the most famous singer not in Europe but in the entire world.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.72,0:46:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你听过我唱歌吗?\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}And have you heard me sing?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.80,0:46:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 没 没有 我没听过  - 当然听过\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- Absolutely. - No, I haven't.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.80,0:46:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 在我看来 你声名远扬\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}But like mine, your reputation precedes you...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.80,0:46:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比起自己的品位我更相信你的名气\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}and well, I trust your reputation more than my own taste, so...{\r}
