Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.95,0:46:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随便问\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Anything.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.39,0:47:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么选我？\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Why me?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.97,0:47:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人们来看我的表演 是为了看我们演出来的东西\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}People come to my show for the pleasure of being hoodwinked.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.31,0:47:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕只有一次 我想让他们看看真实的东西\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Just once, I would love to give them something real.{\r}
