Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.69,1:01:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你们能不能至少打个招呼 - 或者说声再见\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- He couldn't even say hello. - Or goodbye.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.24,1:01:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他要去巡演了 真不好意思 各位\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}He is going on tour. Sorry guys.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.44,1:01:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷静一下 卡莱尔! 自己找个地方待着去吧\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Pull yourself together, Carlyle. Don't you have somewhere to be?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.46,1:01:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是安·惠勒\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Anne Wheeler.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.95,1:01:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴纳姆先生留了一张票给我\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Mr. Barnum said he left a ticket for me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.84,1:01:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I'm sorry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.39,1:01:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我觉得应该是一张 - 不 就是两张\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- I believe this one supposed to be one. - No, there's meant to be two.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.48,1:01:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道告诉你了你会不会来\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Wasn't sure you'd come if I asked.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.15,1:02:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五分钟后开场\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Five minutes to curtains.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.67,1:02:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想到戏院看看\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I've always wanted to go to the theater.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.14,1:02:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菲利普 是你吗?\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Phillip, is that you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.31,1:02:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 爸爸\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Mother. Father.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.52,1:02:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这位是安·惠勒\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}This is Anne Wheeler.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.44,1:02:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菲利普 你就没有一点羞耻心吗?\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Phillip, have you no shame?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.74,1:02:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和巴纳姆一起做生意是一回事\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}To associate yourself with that Barnum business is one thing...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.45,1:02:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是和一个下等人在一起?\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}but parading around with that elf.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.38,1:02:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Anne.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.27,1:02:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么能这么对她说话\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}How dare you speak to her like that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.77,1:02:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你忘了你的地位  - 我的地位?\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- You forget your place, Phillip. - My place?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.94,1:03:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 如果这是我的地位 那我不想要\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Mother, if this is my place, then I don't wanna be a part of it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.63,1:03:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Anne.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.31,1:03:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们是刻薄的人\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}They are small minded people.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.90,1:03:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 为什么你要在乎这些事  - 这些不是小事\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- Why do you care what they say? - It's not just them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.61,1:03:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从来没有人像你父母那样对待我们\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Never had somebody look at you the way your parents looked at me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.93,1:03:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看他们如何看待我们的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}The way everyone would look at us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.61,1:03:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我对你的爱慕\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You know I want you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.49,1:03:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我并不想掩盖这一旦\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}It's not a secret I try to hide.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.70,1:03:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知晓你对我的眷恋\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I know you want me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.20,1:03:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以不要再说我们只是迫于无奈\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}So don't keep saying our hands are tied.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.10,1:03:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你宣称的一切都未尘埃落定\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You claim it's not in the cards.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.24,1:04:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但命运却已经将你远远拖离\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}And fate is pulling you miles away.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.11,1:04:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我失去了触碰你的距离\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}And out of reach from me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.16,1:04:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你却已深藏在我的心里 你若决意谁又能阻挠\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}But you're here in my heart. So who can stop me if I decide{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.88,1:04:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我将你看做是我命运的追寻\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}that you are my destiny?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.03,1:04:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若我们重摹写繁星的轨迹\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}What if we rewrite the stars?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.08,1:04:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把你与我写成命中注定\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Say you were made to be mine.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.01,1:04:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们将永不分离\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Nothing could keep us apart.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.66,1:04:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走上的道路都会通向你\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You'd be the one I was meant to find.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.82,1:04:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切都取决于你我\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}It's up to you, and it's up to me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.44,1:04:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没人可以左右我们的未来\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}No one can say what we get to be.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.91,1:04:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如我们重摹繁星轨迹\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}So why don't we rewrite the stars?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.08,1:04:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或许我们今晚便可以把世界握在手心\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Maybe the world could be ours, tonight.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.61,1:04:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你或许觉得你更容易接近\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You think it's easy?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.66,1:05:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你或许觉得我不想奔向你\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You think I don't want to run to you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.66,1:05:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可连绵的群山\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}But there are mountains.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.11,1:05:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和一道道关卡让我们寸步难行\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}And there are doors that we can't walk through.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.22,1:05:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白你的迷惑不解\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I know you're wondering why.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.59,1:05:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们本来可以融为一体\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Because we're able to be{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.03,1:05:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有你和我 在这有限的空间之中\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Just you and me within these walls.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.34,1:05:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可当我们面对世界的风险 你将会从梦中醒来\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}But when we go outside, you're gonna wake up and see that{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.98,1:05:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到我们的前路一切无望\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}that it was hopeless after all.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.70,1:05:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没人可以把繁星天迹重写\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}No one can rewrite the stars.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.00,1:05:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你又怎么说你将属于我\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}How can you say you'll be mine?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.49,1:05:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这世间的一切都在阻挠着我们\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Everything keeps us apart.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.63,1:05:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我并不是你生命里的唯一\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}And I'm not the one you were meant to find.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.24,1:05:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你无计可施 我也无力改变\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}It's not up to you, it's not up to me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.97,1:05:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当每个人都告诉我们前路暗淡\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}When everyone tells us what we can be.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.91,1:05:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们何以重摹繁星?\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}How can we rewrite the stars?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.74,1:06:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妄言今夜我们会拥有世界\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Say that the world can be ours, tonight.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.11,1:06:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只想与你遨游天际\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}All I want is to fly with you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.11,1:06:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只想伴你一同坠落\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}All I want is to fall with you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.18,1:06:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以放心把你托付与我\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}So just give me all of you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.27,1:06:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 这毫无可能  - 这并非毫无可能\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}It feels impossible It's not impossible.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.33,1:06:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 真的可能?  - 是要你我相信\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Is it impossible? See that it's possible.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.19,1:06:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们怎样重摹繁星?\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}How do we rewrite the stars?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.84,1:06:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来让你成我的命中注定\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Say you were made to be mine?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.54,1:06:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再无什么可以让我分离\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Nothing can keep us apart.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.26,1:06:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为你就是我走向的唯一\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Cause you are the one I was meant to find.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.20,1:06:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切都在你 也在我的手中掌握\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}It's up to you, and it's up to me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.70,1:06:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没人可以左右我们的未来\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}No one can say what we get to be.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.61,1:06:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就让我们重摹繁星轨迹\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}And why don't we rewrite the stars?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.66,1:06:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让这世界尽归我们掌握\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Changing the world to be ours.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.37,1:07:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我对你的爱慕\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You know I want you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.11,1:07:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这并不是需要隐藏的秘密\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}It's not a secret I try to hide.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.36,1:07:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我却无法拥有你\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}But I can't have you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.83,1:07:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们注定要分离\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}We're bound to break and my hands are tied.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.95,1:07:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先是把房子买在和我父母同一条街\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}First it was buying a house on the same street as my parents.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.90,1:07:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,觐见英国女王\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Then meeting the queen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.28,1:07:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把珍妮·林德带到美国来 然后是和我父亲那晚的事\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Then bringing Jenny Lind, and my father the other night.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.72,1:07:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些都不能让你知足么\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}When will it ever be enough for you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.24,1:07:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我做这些都是为了卡洛琳和海伦\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I am doing this for Caroline and Helen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.57,1:07:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 看看你周围 她们什么都有\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Look around you. They have everything.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.53,1:07:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-  你不明白 - 我懂\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- You don't understand. - I do.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.03,1:07:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 你根本不明白!\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}No. You don't understand!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.91,1:07:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么可能明白?\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}How could you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.20,1:08:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们都瞧不起我父亲\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}My father was treated like dirt.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.78,1:08:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也瞧不起我\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I was treated like dirt.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.20,1:08:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我的孩子绝对不会受到这种待遇\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}My children will not be.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.46,1:08:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不需要让所有人喜欢你\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You don't need everyone to love you, Phin.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.37,1:08:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么几个人喜欢你就够了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Just a few good people.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.61,1:08:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道这道理\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I know that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.24,1:08:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 谢谢 - 先生请上车\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- Thank you. - Sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.49,1:08:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要走\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}No. Daddy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.45,1:08:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸！\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Daddy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.57,1:08:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Daddy, no. Wait.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.61,1:08:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 爸爸 - 驾\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- Daddy. - Go.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.17,1:08:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等 不！\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Wait, Daddy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.95,1:08:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一些人想要 一个简简单单 按部就班的人生\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Some people long for a life that is simple and planned.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.66,1:08:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被束缚也是心甘\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Tied with a ribbon.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.06,1:08:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一些人不愿远航\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Some people won't sail the sea{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.01,1:08:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为陆地安全得多\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}'cause they're safer on land.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.57,1:08:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们屈服于自己的命运\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}To follow what's written.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.97,1:09:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我愿与你同行\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}But I'd follow you{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.41,1:09:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,探索无穷的未知\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}to the great unknown.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.66,1:09:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奔向那以\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Off to a world{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.19,1:09:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们为名的世界\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}we call our own.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.91,1:09:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巅峰低谷 起起伏伏\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Mountains and valleys, and all that will come in between{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.53,1:09:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无边无际的沙漠与海洋\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}desert and ocean{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.93,1:09:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你我卷入并陶醉在梦中\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}you pull me in{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.55,1:09:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永不停歇\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}and together we're lost in a dream.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.45,1:09:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我毫无保留\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Always in motion so I risk it all{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.08,1:09:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只为和你在一起\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}just to be with you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.66,1:09:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毫无保留\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}And I risk it all{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.16,1:09:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了我们选择的人生\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}for this life we choose.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.53,1:09:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紧握我的双手 向我保证 永不松开\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Hand in my hand and you promised to never let go.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.70,1:10:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们像走在钢丝上\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}We're walking the tightrope.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.24,1:10:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,悬在高高的天空中\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}High in the sky.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.95,1:10:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,俯瞰着世界\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}We can see the whole world down below.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.57,1:10:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们像走在钢丝上\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}We're walking the tightrope.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.66,1:10:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,充满了未知与可能\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Never sure,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.83,1:10:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我坠下 你会不会将我紧紧抱住?\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}will you catch me if I should fall?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.66,1:10:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是个冒险 其间美景非凡\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Well, it's all an adventure that comes with a breathtaking view.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.61,1:10:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和你一起 走在钢丝上\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Walking the tightrope{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.07,1:10:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和你一起\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}with you{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.91,1:11:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}with you{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.41,1:11:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}with you{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.78,1:11:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}with you{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.95,1:11:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}with you{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.83,1:11:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}with you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.41,1:11:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“仿佛这是我们第一次\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}"It is as though we've learned for the first time..."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.18,1:11:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,领会什么是真正的歌唱\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}what singing really is.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.33,1:11:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,林德小姐值得整个国家最高的尊敬 和最热烈的喝彩\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Miss Lind deserves our nation's highest esteem and lavish ovations.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.16,1:12:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 嗯 我… - 全世界就在我们脚下\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- I mean... - The world at our feet.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.57,1:12:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在 巴纳姆先生\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Well, Mr. Barnum.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.45,1:12:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}This...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.16,1:12:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来为\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}is...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.74,1:12:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梦想成真举杯\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}to making dreams come true.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.03,1:12:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 珍妮\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Thank you, Jenny.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.99,1:12:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,演出剩下不多了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}It's two hours to curtains.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.37,1:12:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我给了你所有 不是么?\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I've given you the world, haven't I?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.53,1:12:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想我该走了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I, I should go.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.49,1:12:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我对你没有好处 我很抱歉 珍妮\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I have become a distraction. I'm sorry, Jenny.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.03,1:12:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 不 你不需要我进行巡演 - 什么 你要离开?\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- You should finish your tour without me. - What? You're leaving?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.87,1:12:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 嗯 行程已经安排妥当了 - 就这样?\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- The itinerary is well in hand. - So that's it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.33,1:12:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你什么意思?\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}What do you mean?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.53,1:12:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是你达到目的的另一个棋子\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I'm just another your acts.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.87,1:12:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我不做了 - 珍妮 珍妮\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- Jenny. - I'm done.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.57,1:13:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,珍妮 不要这样\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Jenny, Jenny, please.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.91,1:13:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你必须要完成巡演\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You have to finish the tour.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.95,1:13:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 必须? - 否则这会毁了我的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- Must I? - It will ruin me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.57,1:13:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当你对其他人不闻不问 巴纳姆先生\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}When you're careless with other people Mr Barnum...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.86,1:13:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你毁了你自己\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}you bring ruin upon yourself.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.61,1:13:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我赔上了我的所有 - 我也同样\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- I have risked everything. - Well, so did I.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.37,1:13:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来我们都亏了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}And seems we've both lost.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.83,1:13:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜空中你我摘下的星星\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}All the stars we steal{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.76,1:13:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永远不足够\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}from the night sky.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.61,1:13:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们永远不足够\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Will never be enough{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.74,1:13:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永远不足够\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}never be enough.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.03,1:13:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成堆的金钱仍然太少\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Towers of gold are still too little.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.78,1:13:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这双手能拥有全世界\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}These hands could hold the world{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.20,1:13:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是却不能满足你的心\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}but it will never be enough{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.83,1:13:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永远不能\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}never be enough.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.28,1:14:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.95,1:14:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么?\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}What was that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.24,1:14:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是再见\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}That was goodbye.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.57,1:14:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你们的到场\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Thank you very much for coming.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.81,1:14:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 请分享给你们的朋友和家人 - 多么精彩的演出啊\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- Say your fancy neighbors. - What a beautiful show.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:50.73,1:14:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁享受这场盛宴? 你? 还是你?\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Who enjoyed yourselves? You?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.87,1:14:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请告诉所有人这马戏团有多精彩\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Tell everyone how much fun you{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:54.51,1:14:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每晚都有新花样\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}had at the circus. New acts every night.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.45,1:14:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,领班!\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Hey, ringmaster.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.11,1:15:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生们 我想请求你们离开\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Gentlemen, I am gonna have to ask you to leave.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.33,1:15:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们的小镇 伙计\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}This is our town, son.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.33,1:15:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该走的是你们 你\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}We think you should leave, you and your freaks.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.97,1:15:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和你的那些怪物朋友们\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}And yours spooks.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.57,1:15:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.07,1:15:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最后说一遍 请你离开\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I will only ask once more.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:17.93,1:15:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否则你能拿我怎样?\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Then what, boy?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.27,1:15:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,揍他们\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Attack.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.53,1:15:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 爸爸\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Daddy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.73,1:16:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姑娘们 孩子 孩子\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- Daddy. Daddy! - Girls.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:04.62,1:16:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们竟然长了那么多了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You have grown so much.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.06,1:16:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“你怎么回来早了些?” - 我想你们了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}What made you decide to come back early?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.91,1:16:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想你\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I missed you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.59,1:16:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-  听起来像是你的托词  - 着火了!\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- That sounds lawful. - Fire.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.05,1:16:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让开 着火了 快点! 是马戏团那边的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- Out of the way. Fire! - Hurry, it's coming from the circus.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.18,1:16:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 着火了! - 跟我来 来 快点\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Girls, stay with me. Come, quickly.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.33,1:16:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家听好了 跟紧点\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Everyone! Stay close.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.00,1:16:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菲利普 菲利普 菲利普 大家都出来了么?\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Phillip, is everyone out?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.46,1:16:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家还好么? 动物们呢?\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Is everyone okay? The animals?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.32,1:16:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们把他们放走了 别无选择\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}We set them free. What else could we do?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.98,1:16:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- W·D 安在哪? - 她在哪? 她在哪?\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- WD, where is Anne? - Where is Anne?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.22,1:16:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不! 菲利普 不!\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}No, Phillip.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.35,1:16:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菲利普! 不 你不能进去\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}No. Stop. You can not go inside.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.41,1:16:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,继续抽水\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Keep pumping.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.32,1:17:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- W·D! - 在这儿 他在这儿\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- WD. - There she is.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.91,1:17:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 菲利普 菲利普 - 爸爸\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- Phillip. - Daddy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.17,1:17:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸!\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- No dad. - Daddy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.43,1:17:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}No.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.87,1:17:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请退后\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Stay back, please.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.58,1:17:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Daddy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.18,1:17:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,担架快来!\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Stretcher, stretcher.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.39,1:17:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他吸入太多的烟 但他还活着 快走\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}He has taken a lot of smoke. He's still breathing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.79,1:17:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来把他抬上担架!\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Let's get him on.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.35,1:18:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抬起来\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.58,1:18:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若我们重摹繁星轨迹\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}What if we rewrite the stars?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.84,1:18:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把你我写成命中注定\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Say you were meant to be mine?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.31,1:18:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永不分离\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Nothing can keep us apart{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.86,1:19:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我注定要与你相逢\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}you are the one I was meant to find.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.40,1:19:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们走\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Here we go.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.88,1:19:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快 就在前面\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Come on, straight ahead.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.08,1:19:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你是来幸灾乐祸的 那请便吧 我不会回嘴的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}If you had come to gloat I wouldn't.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.00,1:19:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们抓住了放火的那些人\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}They caught the thugs who started the fire.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:44.09,1:19:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想你会感兴趣\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I thought you'd like to know.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.65,1:19:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我从没有喜欢过你的演出\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I never liked your show.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.78,1:20:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我一直认为人们的确是喜欢看的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}But I always thought the people did.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.37,1:20:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在也是如此\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}They do.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.59,1:20:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我并不会它称之为艺术\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Mind you, I wouldn't call it art.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.34,1:20:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然不\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Of course not.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.38,1:20:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}But...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.93,1:20:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把各种各样的人拉上舞台\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Putting folks of all kinds on stage.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.00,1:20:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各种肤色 体型 身高的人 一视同仁…\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}All colors, shapes, sizes. Presenting them as equals.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.57,1:20:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他的评论家或许会称这为\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Another critic might have even called it{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.05,1:20:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“人性的礼赞”\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}'a celebration of humanity'.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:38.88,1:20:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会中意这说法的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I would have liked that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:45.01,1:20:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我期望你能重建马戏团\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Well, I hope you'll rebuild.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.47,1:20:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通过珍妮的巡演 我们能有些盈余\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Thank god for Jenny's tour. We can borrow off the profits.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.63,1:20:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能挺过去的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}We'll be fine.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:52.98,1:20:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道那回事儿么?\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You don't know?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.66,1:21:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很抱歉\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I'm sorry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.43,1:21:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丑闻缠身的巴纳姆\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Charity?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.80,1:21:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏瑞蒂 天哪 夏瑞蒂\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Oh God, Charity.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.22,1:21:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我… - 我不想跟你说话\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- I am... - I don't wanna talk to you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.89,1:21:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 什么事都没有发生 - 是么\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- Nothing happened. - Ouch, nothing happened.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.54,1:21:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每张报纸都在刊登这个事情\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}It's on the cover of every paper in New York.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.34,1:21:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是她谋划的 我并不爱她\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Because she orchestrated the photo. I am not in love with her.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.89,1:21:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然不\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Of course you're not.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.42,1:21:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是为了她 不是我或任何其他人\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Not with her, not with me, not with anyone.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:30.67,1:21:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是为了你自己和你的演出\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Just you and your show.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.20,1:21:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要干什么?\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}What are you doing?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.50,1:21:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要回家\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I'm going home.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.33,1:21:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这才是你家\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}This is your home.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.63,1:21:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,银行\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}The bank..{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.84,1:21:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,银行把我们赶出去了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}They are evicting us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:51.27,1:21:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么不跟我商量?\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Why didn't you ask me before?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.90,1:21:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会同意的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I would have said yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.39,1:22:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我从不怕什么风险 只要我们能一同面对\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I never minded the risk, but we always did it together.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.95,1:22:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我估摸你会来这儿的 自怨自哀\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Figured you'd end up here. Feeling sorry for yourself?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.14,1:23:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他们来讨要酬劳 我一分钱都没了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Folks if you have come to get paid, the money's gone. All of it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.48,1:23:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 付不起 - 他妈的别说了 巴纳姆\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- Nothing left to give... - Shut up, Barnum.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:06.35,1:23:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你根本不理解我们\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You just don't get it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:09.28,1:23:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就连我们的母亲都视我们为耻辱\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Our own mothers were ashamed of us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.45,1:23:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她们试图掩盖我们的存在\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Hid us our whole lives.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.29,1:23:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你把我们救出阴霾的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Then you pull us out of the shadows.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.42,1:23:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但现在就连你也要放弃我们\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}And now you are giving upon us too.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.55,1:23:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许你是个骗子\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Maybe you are fraud.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.06,1:23:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许你做这些只是为了金钱\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Maybe it was just about making a buck.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.64,1:23:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你给我们了一个真正的家\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}But you gave us a real family.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.81,1:23:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个马戏团…\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}And the circus...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.82,1:23:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是我们的家\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}That was our home.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.90,1:23:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要重建我们的家\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}We want our home back.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.58,1:23:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看到太阳散失光芒\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I saw the sun begin to dim.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.73,1:23:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我感到冬日彻骨的寒风\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}And felt that winter wind blow cold.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.09,1:24:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个人终于找到他的归属\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}A man learns who is there for him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.68,1:24:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当闪烁的光亮暗淡 当坚实的后盾倒塌\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}When the glitter fades and the walls won't hold.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.98,1:24:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为从那时起留下的只有碎石瓦砾\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}'Cause from then, rubble{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.90,1:24:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留下的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}one remains.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.53,1:24:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有我真正拥有的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Can only be once true.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.62,1:24:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果丧失所有\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}If all was lost.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:21.92,1:24:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能够得到更多\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}There's more I gained.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.80,1:24:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那一定是因为\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Cause it led me back{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.43,1:24:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你回到了我的身边\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}to you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.72,1:24:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我曾与皇室共饮香槟\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I drank champagne with kings and queens{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:55.34,1:24:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,政客颂扬我的大名\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}the politicians praised my name.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:01.35,1:25:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然而那都是别人的梦\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}But those are someone else's dreams.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.14,1:25:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是对我的诱惑和考验\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}The pitfalls of the man I became.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.42,1:25:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,年复一年 我渴望他们的赞扬\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}For years and years I chased their cheers.{\r}
