Dialogue: 0,1:30:54.72,1:30:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 银行拒绝了? - 嗯 不止一次地坚定地回绝了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- The bank said no? - Emphatically. And repeatedly.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.93,1:31:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得全国没有一家银行\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I don't think there is a bank left in this country...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.04,1:31:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愿意借给我们钱了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I can fool into loaning me more money, so...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:07.82,1:31:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉让你们失望了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I'm really sorry to disappoint you all.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:10.19,1:31:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别担心 我们都习惯了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Don't worry, Barnum. We've gotten used to it by now.{\r}
